      "summary": "Foundation NCAs don't exist yet, but research converges toward generalizable architectures: multi-texture genomic signals, AdaNCA plug-and-play adaptors, CLIP-guided discovery, attention-based ViTCA. Key barriers: architectural mismatch (local vs global), task representation challenges, gradient flow issues. Path forward: self-supervised pretraining, CLIP conditioning, hierarchical multi-scale NCAs, scaling laws research.",
