        "optimization",
        "hybrid-methods"
      ],
      "summary": "Routing problem parallels LLM serving: predictive routers select models based on quality/latency/cost, achieving 60-63% cost reduction. Key strategies: semantic routing, cascade routing (try fast model first), mixture-of-experts. For textures: route to NCAs for real-time/organic (25Hz, 68-8000 params), LCMs for interactive photorealism (<1s, 768\u00d7768), standard diffusion for max quality. Hybrid models (Diff-NCA: 336k params) bridge the gap. Implementation: quality/speed predictors, model zoo infrastructure, cascade routing with learned quality gates.",
